# â™»ï¸ Smart Dustbin Using Arduino

An **Automatic Touchless Smart Dustbin** that detects a person, opens automatically, identifies waste type (Wet/Dry), and segregates it using sensors and servo motors.

---

## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project is designed to improve hygiene and promote proper waste segregation.

The Smart Dustbin:

* Detects a person using an Ultrasonic Sensor
* Opens the lid automatically
* Detects moisture in garbage
* Classifies waste as Wet or Dry
* Separates waste using a servo-based selector mechanism

It is a cost-effective and practical solution for smart waste management systems.

