## âš™ï¸ Working Principle

### 1ï¸âƒ£ Object Detection

The ultrasonic sensor detects if a person is within 30 cm of the dustbin.
If detected, the lid opens automatically using a servo motor.

### 2ï¸âƒ£ Waste Placement

The system waits for 3 seconds to allow the user to place garbage.

### 3ï¸âƒ£ Moisture Detection

The moisture sensor reads analog values (0â€“1023).
These values are converted into percentage (0â€“100%).

### 4ï¸âƒ£ Waste Classification

* Moisture < 40% â†’ Wet Waste
* Moisture â‰¥ 40% â†’ Dry Waste

### 5ï¸âƒ£ Waste Segregation

The selector servo rotates to:

* Wet compartment
* Dry compartment

After 3 seconds, it returns to center position.

### 6ï¸âƒ£ Auto Reset

When the person moves away (>30 cm), the lid closes automatically.

